<br>
As I see it, I think Verant will bring up a new server and ask the populations of at least three (probably four) servers to switch over.  The server pool I see for the next &quot;batch&quot; includes Karana, Veeshan, Prexus, Mith Marr, Bertoxx, and Bristlebane.<br>
<br>
So, with this as a possibility, how are your guilds going to handle this?<br>
<br>
As for The Shrine Knights, we haven't decided yet.  Personally, I not for switching.  However, if the guild decides to make the switch, I will go.<br>
<br>
Jzonn Stormwolf &lt;The Shrine Knights&gt;<br>
