<br>
1)Stay on Karana<br>
<br>
2)Move everyone to New Karana<br>
<br>
3)Do a strategic split with those who wished to setting up a new version of the guild on the new server <br>
<br>
4)Let the individual members decide where they wish to go, and make a new guild on the new server if the movers wish to<br>
<br>
I personally am comfortable on Karana and would want to stay, but am not totally inflexible. <br>
<br>
